) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=3 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci

`url_method` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'get post put and so on',

`url_body` varchar(1022) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'post or put request body',

`creator_dt` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP COMMENT 'creation date of record',

`modify_dt` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP COMMENT 'last modified date of record',

`creator_uid` varchar(45) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL COMMENT 'user who create the record and save user name',

`modify_uid` varchar(45) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL COMMENT 'user who modify the record and save user name',

`is_delete` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0' COMMENT 'all record are deleted logically, 1 is deleted, 0 is valid. all query should be filtered by is_delete=0',

PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,

KEY `idx_ecufu_user_id` (`user_id`) USING BTREE

) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=5 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci

`site_id` int DEFAULT NULL,

`subject_id` int DEFAULT NULL,

`visit_id` int DEFAULT NULL,

`form_id` int DEFAULT NULL,

`recipient` text CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci,

`mail_time` datetime DEFAULT NULL,

`creator_dt` datetime DEFAULT NULL,

`modify_dt` datetime DEFAULT NULL,

`creator_uid` varchar(45) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL,

`modify_uid` varchar(45) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL,

`subject` text CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci COMMENT 'subject',

`content` text CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci COMMENT 'content',

`is_delete` bit(1) DEFAULT b'0',

`alert_type` int DEFAULT NULL,

`phase_id` int DEFAULT NULL,

`created_role_id` int DEFAULT NULL,

`subject_visit_id` int DEFAULT NULL,

`subject_form_id` int DEFAULT NULL,

`visit_sn` int DEFAULT NULL,

`randomize_approve_status` bit(1) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'randomize_approval_alert unique, on/off',

`form_alert_config_id` int DEFAULT NULL,

`status` bit(1) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'when AlertType=14, is RegisterSubject status',

PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,

KEY `fk_formalerthistory_subjectid_subject` (`subject_id`),

CONSTRAINT `fk_formalerthistory_subjectid_subject` FOREIGN KEY (`subject_id`) REFERENCES `eclinical_subject` (`id`) ON DELETE RESTRICT ON UPDATE RESTRICT

) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=20 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci

CREATE TABLE `eclinical_form_completion_timeliness_summary` (

`id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT COMMENT 'id',

`site_code` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT '' COMMENT 'siteCode',

`site_id` int DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'siteId',

`total_form_data_entry_required` int DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'totalFormDataEntryRequired',

`total_form_data_entry_completed` int DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'totalFormDataEntryCompleted',

`completion_rate_of_form` decimal(13,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '(Total Form Data Entry Completed / Total Form Data Entry Required) * 100%, keep 2 decimals\r\n * (已完成录入的form总数/需要录入的form总数) * 100%, 保留两位小数',

`total_elapse_days_of_form_completion` int DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '如果form的提交时间在访视日期之前，则差值计算为0',

`average_elapse_days_of_form_completion` decimal(13,2) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '已完成的form的提交时间和访视日期的差值的累加/已完成的form总数, 保留两位小数',

`maximum_elapse_days_of_form_completion` int DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '当前site表单中需要录入的form和访视日期相比，最大的延迟天数， 在计算差值天数的时候，如果表单未提交则取当天的日期否则取提交的日期',

PRIMARY KEY (`id`)

) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci COMMENT='form_completion_timeliness_summary'

`total_elapse_days_of_form_completion` int DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '如果form的提交时间在访视日期之前，则差值计算为0',

`average_elapse_days_of_form_completion` decimal(13,2) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '已完成的form的提交时间和访视日期的差值的累加/已完成的form总数, 保留两位小数',

`maximum_elapse_days_of_form_completion` int DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '当前site表单中需要录入的form和访视日期相比，最大的延迟天数， 在计算差值天数的时候，如果表单未提交则取当天的日期否则取提交的日期',

CREATE TABLE `eclinical_global_ediary_setting` (

`id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,

`study_id` int NOT NULL,

`site_entry` bit(1) DEFAULT NULL,

`reenterable` bit(1) DEFAULT NULL,

`reenter_duration` int DEFAULT '1',

`editable` bit(1) DEFAULT NULL,

`edit_duration` int DEFAULT NULL,

`status` int DEFAULT '0' COMMENT '0.uncommitted 1.committed',

`creator_dt` datetime DEFAULT NULL,

`modify_dt` datetime DEFAULT NULL,

`creator_uid` varchar(45) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL,

`modify_uid` varchar(45) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL,

`is_delete` bit(1) DEFAULT b'0',

`web_entry` bit(1) DEFAULT b'0',

`editable_visible` bit(1) DEFAULT b'0' COMMENT 'editable button visible',

`token_duration_days` int DEFAULT '60',

`dm_review` bit(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT b'1',

`cra_review` bit(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT b'1',

`safety_review` bit(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT b'1',

PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,

UNIQUE KEY `fk_first_entry_item_id_crfversion` (`study_id`),

KEY `fk_crfform_diarysetting` (`site_entry`),

KEY `fk_crfform_diarysetting_crfversion` (`site_entry`,`study_id`),

CONSTRAINT `fk_global_ediary_setting_study_id_study` FOREIGN KEY (`study_id`) REFERENCES `eclinical_study` (`id`) ON DELETE RESTRICT ON UPDATE RESTRICT

) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci

`manual_query_with_data_revise` bit(1) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Yes/No\r\n * After creation date, if data has change history',

`manual_query_with_data_entered` bit(1) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Yes/No\r\n * Data that is queried has data (not empty)',

`query_age` int DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'query age',

`query_status` int DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'query status',

`query_close_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'query close date',

`open_screen_subject_id` varchar(100) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL,

PRIMARY KEY (`id`)

CREATE TABLE `eclinical_odm_item` (

`id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,

`crf_version_id` int NOT NULL,

`name` text CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci,

`data_type` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL,

`show_caption` bit(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT b'0',

`caption_align` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL,

`length` int DEFAULT NULL,

`digit` int DEFAULT NULL,

`sas_field_name` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL,

`sds_var_name` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL,

`origin` varchar(150) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL,

`comment` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci,

`dateformat` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci,

`sdtm_ts` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci,

`question` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci,

`creator_dt` datetime DEFAULT NULL,

`modify_dt` datetime DEFAULT NULL,

`creator_uid` varchar(45) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL,

`modify_uid` varchar(45) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL,

`is_delete` bit(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT b'0',

`locale` json DEFAULT NULL,

`parent_id` int DEFAULT NULL,

`as_child` bit(1) DEFAULT b'0',

`min_range` int DEFAULT NULL,

`max_range` int DEFAULT NULL,

`min_description` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL,

`max_description` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL,

`multi_select` bit(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT b'0',

`allow_future_date` bit(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT b'0' COMMENT 'if true, edc allow enter the future date.',

`required` bit(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT b'0' COMMENT 'the value of the item is not null',

`affect_form_status` bit(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT b'0' COMMENT 'the field is based on `required`, if the `required` and `affect_form_status` are both true, when the value of the item is null, it will affect the status of form in EDC.',

`help_text` text CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci COMMENT 'if the value of the item is not null, the text will popup in EDC.',

PRIMARY KEY (`id`,`crf_version_id`),

KEY `fk_crfversionid_item_version` (`crf_version_id`),

CONSTRAINT `fk_crfversionid_item_version` FOREIGN KEY (`crf_version_id`) REFERENCES `eclinical_crf_version` (`id`) ON DELETE RESTRICT ON UPDATE RESTRICT

) /*!50100 TABLESPACE `innodb_system` */ ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2202 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci

`locale` json DEFAULT NULL,

`main_language` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT 'en_US',

`locale_list` varchar(300) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT 'en_US',

`resolve_days` int DEFAULT NULL,

`cra_review` bit(1) DEFAULT b'0',

`safty_review` bit(1) DEFAULT b'0',

`date_format` varchar(30) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL,

`time_format` varchar(30) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL,

`item_rule_required` bit(1) DEFAULT b'0',

`item_float_precision` int DEFAULT NULL,

`date_unk_check` varchar(30) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL,

`time_unk_check` varchar(30) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL,

`date_before_now` bit(1) DEFAULT b'0',

`auto_subject_name` bit(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT b'1',

`need_initials` bit(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT b'0',

`enable_register_sub` bit(1) DEFAULT b'1',

`trigger_value` decimal(5,2) DEFAULT '100.00',

`subject_code_editable` bit(1) DEFAULT b'0',

`irt_file_id` int DEFAULT NULL,

`register_system` int NOT NULL DEFAULT '5',

`composition_expression` text CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci,

`dm_review` bit(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT b'1',

`lab_auto_populate` bit(1) DEFAULT b'1',
